parameters: Elmgar actually has a map now! However, there’s not much going on with it at the moment, so you can still use this hub area to travel to any of the interesting locations in town. The one exception is travelling to Skirts and More, check the northern sign to figure out how to do that if you want to see the events for travelling there. Also, the only way to reach the guild at the moment is to use the hub area right now.
Also, you can change text and battle animation speeds in the menu, if you want things faster or slower than the default.
The game now has a paperdoll system for the character! By default it will appear during check appearance, but you can also set it to remain on the screen through the key item "misc settings."

I'm also implementing an alternate way to display text. This will essentially combine multiple text boxes into one larger one. When this happens, character text will have quotation marks surrounding them, and will be in color, to indicate who is speaking.

parameters: \c[25]\fiDid you get a "long" hairstyle? I can't actually check that, so you just have to tell me what style you chose.
\fi\c[25]Would you like to view the scene following the exhibitionism walk around town with Alexandra now? You'll get a prompt for this each time you enter this map until you do.

\fi\c[25]This area will be set up to allow you to quickly view scenes that are somewhat out of the way, and have recently had artwork added to them. Viewing these scenes \fbwill\fb cause stat changes unless otherwise noted, and generally behave as if you encountered said scene normally, so I highly recommend saving before viewing them. The scenes will only be available once you've cleared the dungeon they occur in.

Talk to me from front of stall. Is proper business etiquette.
\c[25]Return tomorrow, I brew more potions, yes.

\fi\c[25]I wrote this scene prematurely for the sixth dungeon. You can view it now without stat changes, until that dungeon is actually set up. The scene was slightly edited to keep the contents of the dungeon secret til then. The scene itself involves femdom and feet.
